# Agent skills authoring

When editing files under `agent-skills/`, follow the canonical authoring spec:

- [agent-skills/schema/README.md](../../agent-skills/schema/README.md) — portable frontmatter, `endorlabs.catalog` extension, contracts, workflows.yaml
- [agent-skills/schema/skill.schema.json](../../agent-skills/schema/skill.schema.json) — machine validation

After changes, run `uv run python devtools/sync_agent_bundle.py`. Shipped bundle `SKILL.md` files must contain **only** portable frontmatter (`name`, `description`, optional `disable-model-invocation`).
